data.description: Charming 2 bed, 1 bath Cape cod home in the heart of Newport featuring large rooms, plenty of storage space, and off-street parking including a 1 car garage. Updated kitchen, including stainless steel appliances. Beautiful primary bathroom on first floor. Entertain on the large deck overlooking the flat, fenced in backyard. This home is on a quiet, no outlet street conveniently located within minutes to shopping, expressways and downtown Cincinnati.
